<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.4.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://colored-dye.github.io/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://colored-dye.github.io/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="en"/><updated>2026-02-18T10:40:31+00:00</updated><id>https://colored-dye.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">colored-dye’s blog</title><subtitle>colored-dye&apos;s blog </subtitle><entry><title type="html">Standup and Xiangsheng</title><link href="https://colored-dye.github.io/blog/2026/standup-xiangsheng/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Standup and Xiangsheng"/><published>2026-02-17T17:06:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-02-17T17:06:00+00:00</updated><id>https://colored-dye.github.io/blog/2026/standup-xiangsheng</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://colored-dye.github.io/blog/2026/standup-xiangsheng/"><![CDATA[<p>脱口秀中，难免会冒犯到观众涉及到的人群。所以为了保险起见，脱口秀演员常用的嘲笑对象是自己。 但是相声不同。虽然同样是常见的喜剧形式，常有捧哏角色承担炮火。</p> <p>这其中的文化渊源蛮值得玩味。</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="no-one-should-read"/><category term="journal"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[something off the top of my head.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">随笔</title><link href="https://colored-dye.github.io/blog/2025/scribbles/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="随笔"/><published>2025-11-26T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2025-11-26T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://colored-dye.github.io/blog/2025/scribbles</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://colored-dye.github.io/blog/2025/scribbles/"><![CDATA[<p>中午去吃了叉烧饭，嚼着嚼着，心觉这叉烧饭太好吃了，感动得有点想哭。</p> <p>最近两个月以来天气变冷了，一楼食堂的质量日渐下滑不能果腹，所以我开始每天中午都去二楼的广东风味窗口吃饭。 多数时候是重复的叉烧饭，偶尔会吃腩仔饭换换胃口。档口的小哥都认识我了，默认我吃叉烧饭。</p> <p>当rebuttal和人际关系的不确定性轰炸我时，还是一碗精致的叉烧饭最能抚慰我的内心。</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="no-one-should-read"/><category term="journal"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[